eZ Lightbox extension README

What is the eZ Lightbox extension?
==================================

   This extension adds support for lightboxes to eZ Publish by adding a
   new eZ Publish module named "lightbox" (including operations, triggers,
   fetch functions). Besides the new modules the extension adds a custom
   content action handler, a new datatype for the eZ Teamroom extension
   and a standard design for the provided items.


