Installation
============

   To install the eZ Lightbox extension please refer to the INSTALL file
   provided by the extension.


Installation
============

Please read the INSTALL file for installation instructions.


Upgrading
=========

Please read the update instructions located in the update folder
of the extension to get further information about how to migrate
from one version to another.


